A method of generating a library of expressed cDNA sequences, comprising the steps of: 

 (1) providing a listing of one or more mRNA sequences in a genome; 

 (2) identifying one or more degenerate motifs that bind to a large proportion of said mRNA sequences; 

 (3) providing one or more multi-targeted primers that are complementary to one or more of said degenerate motifs; and 

 (4) combining said multi-targeted primers with said mRNA sequences in a reverse transcription assay to generate a library of expressed cDNA sequences.
